{"tid":1068740,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"沙維：世盃增至48隊太多","createTime":"2019-03-19T12:21:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T01:05:21.000Z","uid":153600,"like":32,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"87b8c172d9b87b72f7b152a090b43a5e688bf3ad","tid":1068740,"uid":153600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T12:21:39.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=pHv7ulxaPAPTUdGhwq1YMQqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=647a2bef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】前西班牙中場球星沙維表示，國際足協應該放棄將2022年卡塔爾世界盃的球隊數量從32支增加到48支的提議。<br />\n<br />\n由美國、墨西哥和加拿大共同主辦的2026年世界盃，將增加48支參賽隊伍，但國際足協會長恩芬天奴（Gianni Infantino）上周表示，於2022年卡塔爾世界盃就增加球隊數量是「可行的」。不過曾協助西班牙贏得2010年世界盃的前巴塞隆拿球星沙維（Xavi Hernandez）表示，這並不是正確的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n「這是太多了，試想像一下卡塔爾有48支隊伍，我看來並不好。」沙維說，「這仍然是由組織者決定，但是現在卡塔爾正在為32支球隊做好準備，很難為增加更多球隊而做出改變，而且足球有32隊已很好，這已經足夠了。」<br />\n<br />\n如果國際足協和卡塔爾組織方面同意增加球隊數量的提議，這建議將於6月5日在巴黎舉行的國際足協大會上投票表決。"},{"pid":"c14797babf3080afbae4fc584da1ce28fe7a276a","tid":1068740,"uid":13480,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T12:23:52.000Z","msg":"卡塔爾夠球場咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2a76f3f7241e3930900325a6fe3110cd206ed38","tid":1068740,"uid":19638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T12:25:03.000Z","msg":"日頭踢一場 夜晚踢多場囉"},{"pid":"7c1dfdab7c1508f3d7e1a68462ab12cb8def59aa","tid":1068740,"uid":12412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T12:27:56.000Z","msg":"就返啲強國啫，嘈嘈嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a65e9cc27c5471ef34575b89231eeaa3faef3c73","tid":1068740,"uid":180462,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c14797babf3080afbae4fc584da1ce28fe7a276a","tid":1068740,"uid":13480,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-03-19T12:23:52.000Z","msg":"卡塔爾夠球場咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,